{"tid":1224201,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無錯呀各位，你地既抗爭又到左瓶頸位","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T02:48:20.000Z","uid":245409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"969efeeb96ef0d8469ee0bd78af7b10c6fb3db7d","tid":1224201,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"其實係人都知係想徹回<br />\n<br />\n但當暫緩之後，你地係進退兩難<br />\n<br />\n進就好大可能民意會日漸遠去，好似14年咁，而且會有部分隊友離隊，唔好一味硬話不徹回就衝，要守住而家有既籌碼<br />\n<br />\n退就大家都知咩事，可能會彈弓手，而且時日過等你地意意消減，等你地無咁銳果陣再出黎，之後既野呀媽係女人，唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n小心處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3ae73114f201d14786585977234ec70a4ea37c","tid":1224201,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f27482f13fe3651d83c7a146f179611b32dc576","tid":1224201,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}